    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparatuses in which a chain reaction of fissionable material is initiated and controlled as for generation of heat for power or for the production of plutonium from uranium.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
